Package: cat.cog
Title: Cognitive Assessment Scoring with LLMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Soria", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "chrissoria@berkeley.edu")
Description: R interface to the Python cat-cog package. Scores CERAD
    constructional praxis (drawn shape) assessments using LLMs. A thin domain
    wrapper around cat.stack for cognitive test scoring from images.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://chrissoria.github.io/cat-llm/cat.cog/, https://github.com/chrissoria/cat-llm
BugReports: https://github.com/chrissoria/cat-llm/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
